NAME

DBIx::Class::ExtraColumn - extra columns for row

DESCRIPTION

This module allows to specify extra columns in DBIx::Class schema classes.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the perldoc
command.

    perldoc DBIx::Class::ExtraColumn

You can also look for information at:

    Repository
        http://github.com/dionys/dbix-class-extracolumn
    Bug tracker
        http://github.com/dionys/dbix-class-extracolumn/issues

